text: Phryneta macularis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Harold in 1879. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo and Angola.BioLib.cz - Phryneta macularis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1879
